          },
          "_name": "content4",
          "_customHTML": "<section class=\"mbr-section content4\" group=\"Article\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n\n    <mbr-parameters>\n    <!-- Block parameters controls (Blue \"Gear\" panel) -->\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Felső térköz\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"1\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Alsó térköz\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"0\">\n\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Cím\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Alcím\" name=\"showSubtitle\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Gombok\" name=\"showButtons\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Háttérszín\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#335e85\">\n    <!-- End block parameters -->\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"media-container-row\">\n            <div class=\"title col-12 col-md-8\">\n                <h2 mbr-if=\"showTitle\" class=\"align-center pb-3 mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\">A coaching Neked szól, ha...</h2>\n                <h3 mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\" class=\"mbr-section-subtitle align-center mbr-light mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\">\n                    Alakítsd a jövőbeni projektjeidet precíz dizájnnal és tökéletesítsd az előreprogramozott funkciókat.\n                </h3>\n                <div class=\"mbr-section-btn align-center py-4\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\">\n                    <a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"https://mobirise.co\">TUDJ MEG TÖBBET</a>\n                    <a class=\"btn btn-black-outline\" href=\"https://mobirise.co\">ÉLŐ BEMUTATÓ</a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_cid": "vfsajFL48I",
          "_anchor": "content4-13",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {}
        },
        {
          "alias": false,
          "_styles": {
            "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 15px)",
            "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 15px)",
            "background-color": "@bgColor",
            ".counter-container": {
              "color": "#767676",
              "ul": {
                "margin-bottom": "0",
                "li": {
                  "margin-bottom": "1rem",
                  "& when (@stylizedCounters)": {
                    "list-style": "none",
                    "&:before": {
                      "position": "absolute",
                      "left": "0px",
                      "margin-top": "-10px",
                      "padding-top": "3px",
                      "content": "''",
                      "display": "inline-block",
                      "text-align": "center",
                      "margin": "5px 10px",
                      "line-height": "20px",
                      "transition": "all .2s",
                      "color": "contrast(@counterColor)",
                      "background": "@counterColor",
                      "width": "25px",
                      "height": "25px",
                      "border-radius": "50%",
                      "& when (@countersType = 'circle')": {
                        "background": "none",
                        "border": "1px solid @counterColor",
                        "color": "@counterColor"
                      },
                      "& when (@countersType = 'square')": {
                        "border-radius": "0"
                      },
                      "& when (@mark)": {
                        "content": "'✓'"
                      }
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            },
            ".mbr-text": {
              "color": "#ffffff"
            },
            ".mbr-text UL": {
              "text-align": "left"
            }
          },
          "_name": "content12",
          "_customHTML": "<section class=\"mbr-section article content12\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n    <!-- Block parameters controls (Blue \"Gear\" panel) -->\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Felső térköz\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"2\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Alsó térköz\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"2\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Stilizált számlálók\" name=\"stylizedCounters\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Számláló színe\" name=\"counterColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"stylizedCounters\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Stilizált számlálók\" name=\"stylizedCounters\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Jelzés\" name=\"mark\" checked condition=\"stylizedCounters\">\n        <select title=\"Számláló típusa\" name=\"countersType\" condition=\"stylizedCounters\">\n            <option value=\"default\" selected>Kör kitöltés</option>\n            <option value=\"circle\">Kör</option>\n            <option value=\"square\">Négyszög</option>\n        </select>   \n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Háttérszín\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#335e85\">\n    <!-- End block parameters -->\n    </mbr-parameters> \n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"media-container-row\">\n            <div class=\"mbr-text counter-container col-12 col-md-8 mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" data-multiline mbr-article>\n                <ul>\n                    <li>úgy érzed, elakadtál egy fontos élethelyzetben</li><li>döntés előtt állsz, és szeretnél tisztábban látni</li><li>életközépi változásokat tapasztalsz</li><li>csökkent a munkahelyi motivációd</li><li>párkapcsolati vagy önismereti kérdések foglalkoztatnak</li><li>szeretnél tudatosabban jelen lenni az életedben</li>\n                </ul>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_cid": "vfsbaJ1T2r",
          "_anchor": "content12-14",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {}
        },
        {
          "alias": false,
          "_styles": {
            "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 15px)",
            "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 15px)",
            "& when (@bg-type = 'color')": {
              "background": "linear-gradient(45deg, @bg-value, @color2)"
            },
            "& when (@bg-type = 'image')": {
              "background-image": "url(@bg-value)"
            },
            ".list-group-item": {
              "padding": ".75rem 3.25rem"
            },
            ".plan": {
              "word-break": "break-word",
              "position": "relative",
              "max-width": "300px",
              "padding-right": "0",
              "padding-left": "0",
              "color": "#767676",
              ".list-group-item": {
                "position": "relative",
                "-webkit-justify-content": "center",
                "justify-content": "center",
                "border": "0",
                "&::after": {
                  "position": "absolute",
                  "bottom": "0",
                  "left": "20%",
                  "width": "60%",
                  "height": "2px",
                  "content": "\"\"",
                  "background-color": "#eaeaea"
                },
                "&:last-child::after": {
                  "display": "none"
                }
              }
            },
            ".plan-header": {
              "padding-left": "1rem",
              "padding-right": "1rem"
            },
            ".plan-header, .plan-body": {
              "background-color": "#fff"
            },
            ".price-figure": {
              "font-weight": "700",
              "color": "#232323"
            },
            ".price-value": {
              "font-weight": "700",
              "vertical-align": "top"
            },
            "@media (max-width: 550px)": {
              ".price-figure": {
                "font-size": "4.25rem"
              }
            }
          },
          "_name": "pricing-tables1",
          "_customHTML": "<section group=\"Pricing Tables\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-parallax-background':bg.parallax}\" class=\"pricing-table1\">\n\n    <mbr-parameters>\n    <!-- Block parameters controls (Blue \"Gear\" panel) -->\n        <input inline type=\"range\" title=\"Felső térköz\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\">\n        <input inline type=\"range\" title=\"Alsó térköz\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\">\n\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Gombok\" name=\"showButtons\" checked>\n        <select title=\"Elemek száma\" name=\"itemsCount\">\n            <option value=\"1\">1</option>\n            <option value=\"2\" selected>2</option>\n            <option value=\"3\">3</option>\n            <option value=\"4\">4</option>\n        </select>\n\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Háttérkép\" value=\"../_images/background2.jpg\">\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Háttérszín\" value=\"#0f7699\" selected>\n            <input type=\"video\" title=\"Háttérvideó\" value=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=36YgDDJ7XSc\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Szín 2\" name=\"color2\" value=\"#efefef\" condition=\"bg.type=='color'\" selected>\n\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Fedés\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Fedőszín\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#232323\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Átlátszóság\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.2\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    <!-- End block parameters -->\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\">\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"media-container-row\">\n\n            <div class=\"plan col-12 mx-2 my-2 justify-content-center\" mbr-if=\"itemsCount > 0\" mbr-class=\"{\n                 'col-lg-4': itemsCount == 3,\n                 'col-lg-6': itemsCount == 2,\n                 'col-lg-3': itemsCount == 4}\">\n                <div class=\"plan-header text-center pt-5\">\n                    <h3 class=\"plan-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".plan-title\">\n                        Egyéni coaching</h3>\n                    <div class=\"plan-price\">\n                        <span mbr-text class=\"price-value mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".price-value\">alkalmanként</span>\n                        <span mbr-text class=\"price-figure mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-1\" data-app-selector=\".price-figure\">\n                              10.000</span>\n                        <small mbr-text class=\"price-term mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".price-term\">\n                            <br>Ft/ 50 perc</small>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"plan-body pb-5\">\n                    <div class=\"plan-list align-center\">\n                        <ul mbr-text class=\"list-group list-group-flush mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n                            <li class=\"list-group-item\">\n                                Rövid leírás a szolgáltatásról</li>\n                            <li class=\"list-group-item\">\n                                személyesen és online</li>\n                        </ul>\n                    </div>\n                    <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" class=\"mbr-section-btn text-center pt-4 \" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\"><a href=\"https://mobirise.co\" class=\"btn btn-primary\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">EZ ÉRDEKEL!</a></div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"plan col-12 mx-2 my-2 justify-content-center\" mbr-if=\"itemsCount > 1\" mbr-class=\"{\n                 'col-lg-4': itemsCount == 3,\n                 'col-lg-6': itemsCount == 2,\n                 'col-lg-3': itemsCount == 4}\">\n                <div class=\"plan-header text-center pt-5\">\n                    <h3 class=\"plan-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".plan-title\">\n                        Egyéni coaching jogi szemlélettel</h3>\n                    <div class=\"plan-price\">\n                        <span mbr-text class=\"price-value mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".price-value\">alkalmanként</span>\n                        <span mbr-text class=\"price-figure mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-1\" data-app-selector=\".price-figure\">\n                            13.000</span>\n                        <small mbr-text class=\"price-term mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".price-term\"><br>Ft/ 50 perc</small>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"plan-body pb-5\">\n                    <div class=\"plan-list align-center\">\n                        <ul mbr-text class=\"list-group list-group-flush mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n                            <li class=\"list-group-item\">\n                                Rövid leírás a szolgáltatásról</li>\n                            <li class=\"list-group-item\">\n                                személyesen és online</li>\n                        </ul>\n                    </div>\n                    <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" class=\"mbr-section-btn text-center pt-4\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\"><a href=\"https://mobirise.co\" class=\"btn btn-primary\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">EZ ÉRDEKEL!</a></div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"plan col-12 mx-2 my-2 justify-content-center\" mbr-if=\"itemsCount > 2\" mbr-class=\"{\n                 'col-lg-4': itemsCount == 3,\n                 'col-lg-6': itemsCount == 2,\n                 'col-lg-3': itemsCount == 4}\">\n                <div class=\"plan-header text-center pt-5\">\n                    <h3 class=\"plan-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".plan-title\">\n                        Prémium\n                    </h3>\n                    <div class=\"plan-price\">\n                        <span mbr-text class=\"price-value mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".price-value\">\n                            $\n                        </span>\n                        <span mbr-text class=\"price-figure mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-1\" data-app-selector=\".price-figure\">\n                            90</span>\n                        <small mbr-text class=\"price-term mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".price-term\">\n                            évente\n                        </small>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"plan-body pb-5\">\n                    <div class=\"plan-list align-center\">\n                        <ul mbr-text class=\"list-group list-group-flush mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n                            <li class=\"list-group-item\">\n                                A Mobirise tökéletes a hozzá nem értőknek, akik nincsenek tisztában a webfejlesztéssel.\n                            </li>\n                            <li class=\"list-group-item\">\n                                15 GB sávszélesség\n                            </li>\n                        </ul>\n                    </div>\n                    <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" class=\"mbr-section-btn text-center pt-4\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\">\n                        <a href=\"https://mobirise.co\" class=\"btn btn-primary\">VEDD MEG MOST</a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"plan col-12 mx-2 my-2 justify-content-center\" mbr-if=\"itemsCount > 3\" mbr-class=\"{\n                 'col-lg-4': itemsCount == 3,\n                 'col-lg-6': itemsCount == 2,\n                 'col-lg-3': itemsCount == 4}\">\n                <div class=\"plan-header text-center pt-5\">\n                    <h3 class=\"plan-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".plan-title\">\n                        Csúcs\n                    </h3>\n                    <div class=\"plan-price\">\n                        <span mbr-text class=\"price-value mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".price-value\">\n                            $\n                        </span>\n                        <span mbr-text class=\"price-figure mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-1\" data-app-selector=\".price-figure\">\n                            150</span>\n                        <small mbr-text class=\"price-term mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".price-term\">\n                            óránként\n                        </small>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"plan-body pb-5\">\n                    <div class=\"plan-list align-center\">\n                        <ul mbr-text class=\"list-group list-group-flush mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n                            <li class=\"list-group-item\">\n                                A Mobirise tökéletes a hozzá nem értőknek, akik nincsenek tisztában a webfejlesztéssel.\n                            </li>\n                            <li class=\"list-group-item\">\n                                20 GB sávszélesség\n                            </li>\n                        </ul>\n                    </div>\n                    <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" class=\"mbr-section-btn text-center pt-4\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\">\n                        <a href=\"https://mobirise.co\" class=\"btn btn-primary\">VEDD MEG MOST</a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_cid": "vfsGHmpFKN",
          "_anchor": "pricing-tables1-1b",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {}
        },
        {
          "alias": false,
          "_styles": {
            "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 15px)",
            "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 15px)",
            "& when (@bg-type = 'color')": {
              "background-color": "@bg-value"
            },
            "& when (@bg-type = 'image')": {
              "background-image": "url(@bg-value)"
            },
            ".mbr-iconfont": {
              "font-size": "48px",
              "padding-right": "1rem"
            },
            ".icon-block": {
              "margin-bottom": "10px",
              ".icon-block__icon": {
                "display": "inline-block",
                "vertical-align": "middle"
              },
              ".icon-block__title": {
                "display": "inline-block",
                "vertical-align": "middle",
                "margin-bottom": "0",
                "line-height": "1",
                "font-style": "italic"
              }
            },
            ".mbr-text": {
              "color": "#767676"
            },
            "textarea.form-control": {
              "min-height": "100px"
            },
            "a:not([href]):not([tabindex])": {
              "color": "#fff",
              "border-radius": "3px"
            },
            ".google-map": {
              "height": "~\"@{heightMap}rem\"",
              "position": "relative",
              "iframe": {
                "height": "100%",
                "width": "100%"
              },
              "[data-state-details]": {
                "color": "#6b6763",
                "font-family": "Montserrat",
                "height": "1.5em",
                "margin-top": "-0.75em",
                "padding-left": "1.25rem",
                "padding-right": "1.25rem",
                "position": "absolute",
                "text-align": "center",
                "top": "50%",
                "width": "100%"
              },
              "&[data-state]": {
                "background": "#e9e5dc"
              },
              "&[data-state=\"loading\"]": {
                "[data-state-details]": {
                  "display": "none"
                }
              }
            },
            "@media (max-width: 767px)": {
              "h2": {
                "padding-top": "2rem"
              }
            },
            "@media (min-width: 768px)": {
              ".container > .row > .col-md-6": {
                "&:first-child": {
                  "padding-right": "30px"
                },
                "&:last-child": {
                  "padding-left": "30px"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "_name": "form4",
          "_customHTML": "<section class=\"mbr-section form4\" group=\"Forms\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n\n    <mbr-parameters>\n    <!-- Block parameters controls (Blue \"Gear\" panel) -->\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Felső térköz\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"8\" value=\"3\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Alsó térköz\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"8\" value=\"3\">\n\n        <input type=\"map\" title=\"Térkép\" name=\"googleMap\" place-id=\"iframe\" value=\"<iframe src=&quot;https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d2694.3012434496227!2d21.612542812417534!3d47.52299789362611!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x47470e139f26c937%3A0x5965a7c379d42095!2sDebrecen%2C%20Postakert%20u.%2016a%2C%204025!5e0!3m2!1shu!2shu!4v1774967923900!5m2!1shu!2shu&quot; width=&quot;600&quot; height=&quot;450&quot; style=&quot;border:0;&quot; allowfullscreen=&quot;&quot; loading=&quot;lazy&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer-when-downgrade&quot;></iframe>\">\n        <input type=\"range\" title=\"Height Map\" name=\"heightMap\" min=\"15\" max=\"50\" step=\"1\" value=\"25\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Cím\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Ikonok\" name=\"showIcons\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Fejléc alcím\" name=\"showSubheading\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Kapcsolatok\" name=\"showContacts\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Alcím\" name=\"showSubtitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Szöveg\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Űrlap\" name=\"showForm\" checked>\n\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Háttérkép\" value=\"../_images/background3.jpg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Háttérszín\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n            <input type=\"video\" title=\"Háttérvideó\" value=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uNCr7NdOJgw\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Fedés\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Fedőszín\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#efefef\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Átlátszóság\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.9\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    <!-- End block parameters -->\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\">\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"row\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-6\">\n                <div class=\"google-map\" mbr-map=\"googleMap\">\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-md-6\">\n                <h2 mbr-if=\"showTitle\" class=\"pb-3 align-left mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\">\n                    Írj egy pár sort\n                </h2>\n                <div>\n                    <div class=\"icon-block pb-3 align-left\">\n                        <span mbr-if=\"showIcons\" class=\"icon-block__icon\">\n                            <span mbr-icon class=\"mbri-letter mbr-iconfont\"></span>\n                        </span>\n                        <h4 mbr-if=\"showSubheading\" class=\"icon-block__title align-left mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".icon-block,.icon-block .icon-block__title\">\n                            Lépj kapcsolatba velem &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</h4>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"icon-contacts pb-3\" mbr-if=\"showContacts\">\n                        <h5 mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" class=\"align-left mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">Érdeklődésed és bejelentkezésed az alábbi elérhetőségeimen várom:</h5>\n                        <p mbr-if=\"showText\" class=\"mbr-text align-left mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\">\n                            Telefon: +36-30-527-4491&nbsp;<br>\n                            Email: info@elekaniko.hu</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div mbr-form mbr-if=\"showForm\">\n                    <!---Formbuilder Form--->\n                    <form action=\"aniko.elek@gmail.com\" name=\"Mobirise Form\" method=\"POST\" class=\"mbr-form form-with-styler\">\n                        <div class=\"row\">\n                            <div hidden=\"hidden\" data-form-alert class=\"alert alert-success col-12\">Kedves Érdeklődő!\n\nÜzeneted ezúton is köszönöm, melyre 1 munkanapon belül válaszolok!\n\nÜdvözlettel:\n\nDr. Elek Anikó\ncoach és jogász</div>\n                            <div hidden=\"hidden\" data-form-alert-danger class=\"alert alert-danger col-12\">\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"dragArea row\">\n                            <div class=\"col-md-6  form-group\" data-for=\"name\">\n                                <input type=\"text\" name=\"name\" placeholder=\"Neved\" data-form-field=\"Name\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" required=\"required\" class=\"form-control input\">\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"col-md-6  form-group\" data-for=\"phone\">\n                                <input type=\"text\" name=\"phone\" placeholder=\"Telefonszámod\" data-form-field=\"Phone\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" required=\"required\" class=\"form-control input\">\n                            </div>\n                            <div data-for=\"email\" class=\"col-md-12  form-group\">\n                                <input type=\"text\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"E-mail címed\" data-form-field=\"Email\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" class=\"form-control input\" required=\"required\">\n                            </div>\n                            <div data-for=\"message\" class=\"col-md-12  form-group\">\n                                <textarea name=\"message\" placeholder=\"Üzenet\" data-form-field=\"Message\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" class=\"form-control input\"></textarea>\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"col-md-12 input-group-btn  mt-2 align-center\" mbr-buttons=\"true\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-mbrBtnLink,-mbrBtnAdd\">\n                                <a type=\"submit\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-form\">ÜZENET KÜLDÉSE</a>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </form><!---Formbuilder Form--->\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_cid": "vfrfM1cziv",
          "_anchor": "form4-r",
